<div align="center">
    <h1>EmotiVoice üòä: a Multi-Voice and Prompt-Controlled TTS Engine</h1>
</div>

<div align="center">
    <a href="./README.zh.md"><img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/README-‰∏≠ÊñáÁâàÊú¨-red"></a>
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
